Content: [dscrdvrsc] <gigamesh> i dont mean to sound ungrateful, even though I am. A "tip" of 1 cent is hardly amusing, and irregardless I will buy more VRSC. **What I am saying** is that tipping new community members such minuscule sums is not good. Better to not tip at all. While the price rests at $0.10 per coin it is (IMHO) abhorrent that anybody should tip  amounts less than that, particularly when coupled with risible comments. This community is about to explode, and if the incumbents cant appreciate the interests of new members over the value of 1 penny, then the the cypherpunk roots of this coin are *truly* compromised.
